1) Create an arithmetic circuit that takes signals xâ‚, xâ‚‚, ..., xâ‚™ and is satisfied if at least one signal is 0.

x1(x1 - 1) === 0
x2(x2 - 1) === 0
...xn(xn-1)=== 0
Z === (x1 + x2...xn) - 2(x1*x2*...xn)

2) Create an arithmetic circuit that takes signals xâ‚, xâ‚‚, ..., xâ‚™ and is satsified if all signals are 1.

